Troubleshooting Common Issues
Issue 1: Nginx Configuration Errors
If Nginx fails to start, check the configuration:

sudo nginx -t
sudo systemctl status nginx
sudo journalctl -u nginx -f
Issue 2: iptables Rules Not Persisting
To ensure iptables rules persist after reboot:

sudo apt install iptables-persistent -y
sudo netfilter-persistent save
Issue 3: Tor Hidden Service Not Generating
If hidden service addresses aren't generated:

sudo systemctl stop tor
sudo rm -rf /var/lib/tor/c2_service/
sudo rm -rf /var/lib/tor/direct_c2/
sudo systemctl start tor
sleep 30
sudo cat /var/lib/tor/c2_service/hostname
Issue 4: Port Conflicts
Check for port conflicts:

sudo netstat -tlnp | grep -E ':(80|443|8080|9050)'
sudo lsof -i :80
